Experiment 3: Slideshow

Aim
To develop an Android application that displays images as a slideshow using ImageView and Handler.

Algorithm
1.Start Android Studio and create a new project.
2.Add ImageView in the activity_main.xml layout.
3.Place images in the drawable folder.
4.Create an array of images in MainActivity.
5.Declare a Handler to control the time delay.
6.Create a Runnable method to change images.
7.Use setImageResource() to display images.
8.Use postDelayed() to change the image every few seconds.
9.Run the application.
10.Images will automatically change like a slideshow.
